tweets.content: @OpenDataWatch: Three takeaways from the #IODC16 on linking national statistical offices and the #opendata community http://bit.ly/2dm9ArT
@OpenDataWatch: Our session on national statistical offices and open data begins now in the main room of #IODC16pic.twitter.com/3tSbl9JKcq

info: This session was aimed at looking into the very challenging intersection between open data and official statistics and how to build bridges between the two communities so they both can take advantage of each other.
conference_notes: Shaida Baidee closed this session highlighting the bright future that is ahead as a result of linking the open data community and National Statistical Offices.
name: Data + National Statistical Offices
